summary: The document is a classified communication concerning the release of information under the President John F. Kennedy Assassination Records Act of 1992. It references an incomplete document related to traces on Lee Harvey Oswald and includes a request for the deletion of certain crypts before its release. Additionally, the communication seeks to be informed about the release date of these documents.
key_findings: The document pertains to the release of records under the President John F. Kennedy Assassination Records Act of 1992.
It mentions an incomplete document regarding Lee Harvey Oswald.
There is a specific request to delete certain crypts prior to the document's release.
The communication also requests updates on the release date of the documents in question.
